com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport

Class ItemTypeCount

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.searchservice.transport.ItemTypeCount

  • public final class ItemTypeCount
extends Object
    Information about the number of Items of a particular ItemType, and (optionally) at a particular location in a dumbbell.
    Since:
    1.0

        public DumbbellPart getDumbbellPart()
        Gets the DumbbellPart identifying the location in dumbbells of the Items to which the count refers.
        Returns:
        See above. If the count does not refer to Items in dumbbells, the return value is DumbbellPart.NONE.

        See above, or null if the count is not appropriate.
